@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = paste-access-token-here
@scheduleId = paste-schedule-id-here
@roomId = paste-room-id-here

### 내 일정 목록
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 특정 프로젝트룸 일정 목록
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules?roomId={{roomId}}&page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 기간 기준 일정 목록
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules?from=2026-07-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-08-01T00:00:00Z&page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 개인 일정 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "개인 포트폴리오 정리",
  "startsAt": "2026-07-02T01:00:00Z",
  "endsAt": "2026-07-02T02:00:00Z",
  "allDay": false
}

### 프로젝트룸 일정 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "{{roomId}}",
  "title": "클라이언트 중간 리뷰",
  "startsAt": "2026-07-03T05:00:00Z",
  "endsAt": "2026-07-03T06:00:00Z",
  "allDay": false
}

### 일정 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "클라이언트 중간 리뷰 준비",
  "startsAt": "2026-07-03T04:30:00Z",
  "endsAt": "2026-07-03T06:00:00Z",
  "allDay": false
}

### 일정 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/schedules/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
